    "metaDescription": "LED walls for churches and live events — pixel pitch, processors, signal flow, ProPresenter integration, and why custom pixel graphics are the thing nobody tells you about until you're already installed.",
    "excerpt": "An LED wall is transformational when specced right and a continuous frustration when specced wrong. After years of installing them in churches and live venues, here's everything I wish someone had put in one place.",
    "image": "/images/blog/neewer-660-rgb-led-panel-hero.jpg",
